    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This can help dig into the logs for a spec file.  You can do one of these two things (both is overkill)</p>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/4339818.js'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>describe &quot;Something&quot;
  before(:each) do |x|
    Rails.logger.info &quot;RspecExample: &quot; + x.example.metadata[:full_description]
  end
end</code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>
